metadata.name: Frogville Fiends
metadata.description:
Emerging out of a Mouf, you will be greeted by the Fiends of Frogville. Everyone including Mr. Rabbit, Longcow, Detective Duck, and The Frog King will have stories to tell, and trinkets to sell. Just be careful crossing the bridge...

Original artwork by Mobsolete - 5400x5400px - PNG - 300DPI 

Featuring Visitor #4029 and Visitor #2171 from Mike Mitchell's "The Visitors"
